txt.en: You have made a good start, but there is yet much work to be done, if the Zhélruka hope to settle in the formidable Grey Mountains.
You have made a good start, but there is yet much work to be done, if the Zhélruka hope to settle in the formidable Grey Mountains.

Lend a hand in Skarháld by assisting Stráhek the Stout and by completing Wanted Pebbles quests.\n\n<rgb=#FF00FF>Completing this quest will unlock Reclaiming the Grey III, and can be replayed weekly. This quest will be removed on the weekly reset time, and so must be completed weekly by that time.</rgb>
